    "<strong>Allow a full day.</strong> Pair Mystic Seaport (morning) with Mystic Aquarium (afternoon) — buy the <strong>Mystic Pass</strong> in advance for a combined discount on both. Park downtown for free at the public garage on Holmes Street and walk; downtown parking elsewhere is metered and competitive. Eat lunch on Main Street between the two stops.",
